  <title>Two-component signal transduction systems and regulation of virulence factors in Xanthomonas : a perspective</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=e2ad3ad0d5a3d39f4acd16ee28734ecc&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
